basestation.bot

Class BotManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • basestation.bot.BotManager

  • public class BotManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Tracks and manages all bots. Any bot that you create a connection to should be tracked under this manager to prevent errors. Bots are uniquely identified by their names.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      BotManager()
      Initializes the bot manager with a fresh map and counter
